  <entry>
    <title>切片</title>
    <url>/2025/02/01/golang%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B-%E5%88%87%E7%89%87/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="认识切片"><a href="#认识切片" class="headerlink" title="认识切片"></a>认识切片</h2><p>首先要知道，切片不是长度可变的数组，切片本质上是对数组的一个引用，但其大小是动态变化的，不像数组那样固定，切片在golang也是属于引用数据类型。切片的底层实现如图所示：</p>
<p><img src="/golang%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B-%E5%88%87%E7%89%87/202502101043.png" alt="202502101043"></p>
<p>切片的结构体主要包含三个部分：</p>
<ul>
<li>指向底层数组的指针：指向切片所引用的底层数组的内存地址。</li>
<li>切片的长度（len）：切片中包含的元素个数。</li>
<li>切片的容量（cap）：切片所能容纳的元素个数（即从切片的开始位置到底层数组的末尾的元素个数）。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="快速上手"><a href="#快速上手" class="headerlink" title="快速上手"></a><strong>快速上手</strong></h2><p>下面我们来介绍几种切片的创建方式</p>
<figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> main</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="string">&quot;fmt&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">//	方法一，变量声明初始化</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">var</span> slice1 []<span class="type">int</span></span><br><span class="line">	slice1 = []<span class="type">int</span>&#123;<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	fmt.Printf(<span class="string">&quot;方式一，变量声明初始化方式：slice1: %v\n&quot;</span>, slice1)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">//	方法二，短变量声明初始化</span></span><br><span class="line">	slice2 := []<span class="type">int</span>&#123;<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	fmt.Printf(<span class="string">&quot;方法二，短变量声明初始化：slice2: %v\n&quot;</span>, slice2)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">//	方法三，使用make创建</span></span><br><span class="line">	slice3 := <span class="built_in">make</span>([]<span class="type">int</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">	fmt.Printf(<span class="string">&quot;方法三，使用make创建：slice3: %v\n&quot;</span>, slice3)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">//	方法四，从数组中切割创建</span></span><br><span class="line">	arr := [<span class="number">5</span>]<span class="type">int</span>&#123;<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	slice4 := arr[<span class="number">1</span>:<span class="number">3</span>]</span><br><span class="line">	fmt.Printf(<span class="string">&quot;方法四，从数组中切割创建：slice4: %v\n&quot;</span>, slice4)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
